      "message": "If I\u0027m reading the spec right, then number of dst ranges (1 here) needs to match the number of src ranges (fNumSamplers here). Seems like you\u0027ll need to make a one off range for each step in the dst even though they are contiguous. I wonder if it makes it cleaner at all do do this copy in the code above instead of building up the arrays?",
